{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-markdown-page-js","path":"/faq/mixing-by-weight","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"mixing-by-weight\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mixing-by-weight\" aria-label=\"mixing by weight permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Mixing by Weight</h1>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prerequisites\" aria-label=\"prerequisites permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prerequisites</h2>\n<p>All ingredients must be <a href=\"https://www.usp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">USP grade</a> or equivalent.</p>\n<h3 id=\"required\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#required\" aria-label=\"required permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Required</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Vegetable glycerin (VG) in dropper bottle</li>\n<li>Propylene glycol (PG) in dropper bottle</li>\n<li>Flavors in dropper bottles</li>\n<li>A recipe as provided by an online calculator like <a href=\"https://e-liquid-recipes.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ELR</a> or <a href=\"https://alltheflavors.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ATF</a></li>\n<li>Scale, 0.01g readability</li>\n<li>Empty bottle</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"optional\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#optional\" aria-label=\"optional permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Optional</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Nicotine in dropper bottle</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"procedure\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#procedure\" aria-label=\"procedure permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Procedure</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Line the following bottles up next to your scale: Nicotine, PG, VG, and flavors in the order they are listed on the recipe.</li>\n<li>Place the empty bottle on the scale.</li>\n<li>Turn the scale on. Wait for it to read a stable zero grams.</li>\n<li>Find the number of grams of nicotine you need in the recipe. Add that much nicotine to the empty bottle. Tare the scale.</li>\n<li>Find the number of grams of PG you need in the recipe. Add that much PG to the bottle. Tare the scale.</li>\n<li>Find the number of grams of VG you need in the recipe. Add that much VG to the bottle. Tare the scale.</li>\n<li>For each flavor, find the number of grams you need in the recipe. Add that much flavoring to the bottle. Tare the scale.</li>\n<li>Turn off the scale. Take the bottle off the scale.</li>\n<li>Cap the bottle and shake it thoroughly!</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"notes\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#notes\" aria-label=\"notes permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Notes</h2>\n<p>Flavorings must be food-safe, but beyond that there are a variety of food-safe ingredients which should be avoided when making e-liquid. Please check <a href=\"https://safety.diyejuice.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">DIY Flavor Safety</a> for more information on flavors to avoid or limit use of.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/faq/mixing-by-weight","title":"FAQ - Mixing by Weight"}}},"pageContext":{"html":"<h1 id=\"mixing-by-weight\" 